Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.35,0:00:04.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們應該著眼的不是過去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.29,0:00:05.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而是現在
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.32,0:00:08.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,深衣奈
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.93,0:00:11.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果我和你流著相同的血的話
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.53,0:00:15.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不想做出拋棄這樣的行為…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.99,0:00:18.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不想拋棄親人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.35,0:00:19.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麻鬱…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.20,0:00:22.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是我們也可能是外人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.50,0:00:24.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的話怎麼辦？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.73,0:00:26.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那還用說
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.67,0:00:28.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.75,0:00:30.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很羞人的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.57,0:00:31.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.32,0:00:32.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.97,0:00:34.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.96,0:00:39.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裏…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.32,0:00:40.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.74,0:00:45.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來是做夢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.93,0:00:48.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我竟然做這種夢…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.47,0:00:54.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對…對不起！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.47,0:00:56.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是睡糊塗了…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.76,0:00:57.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有那種傾向…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.66,0:00:59.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.84,0:01:01.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這…這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.30,0:01:05.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起…振作點…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.57,0:01:10.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.12,0:01:10.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.88,0:02:38.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)\pos(205,170)\fs40\fn幼圓\3c&H9341a5\bord2}有可能是外人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.36,0:03:01.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一對被褥和最低限度的生活用品
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.08,0:03:02.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,43560円
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.73,0:03:04.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加上消費稅
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.95,0:03:08.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,共45738円
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.03,0:03:14.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這些費用就由你們兩個包攬所有的家務活來還清
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.96,0:03:18.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,具體該如何分工由你們自己決定
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.23,0:03:23.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我用你們做家務的時間做編程的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.86,0:03:25.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.06,0:03:27.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.06,0:03:28.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.36,0:03:31.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有相互間的稱呼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.22,0:03:33.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想直接叫名字比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.58,0:03:37.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不喜歡太過趨緊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.43,0:03:38.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.61,0:03:42.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,叫樺戀、麻鬱？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.30,0:03:43.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.40,0:03:47.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也以深衣奈、樺戀來稱呼你們
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.28,0:03:48.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.08,0:03:50.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.18,0:03:54.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,深衣奈小姐、麻郁先生
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.23,0:03:55.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要加上“先生小姐”
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.53,0:03:58.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.31,0:04:00.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,脖子怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.71,0:04:02.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.79,0:04:04.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請不要問
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.33,0:04:08.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那算了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.65,0:04:13.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼我去房間工作了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.35,0:04:14.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其餘的事就拜託你們了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.09,0:04:18.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,忘記說了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.78,0:04:20.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,電話響了也別去接
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.95,0:04:21.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.83,0:04:31.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來了來了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.03,0:04:32.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我都說了別接！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.87,0:04:36.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.62,0:04:38.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,資料會在今日內傳送給你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.93,0:04:41.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.25,0:04:42.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.90,0:04:46.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要不要做呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.33,0:04:48.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來杯咖啡怎樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.81,0:04:51.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我說過進來前至少要先敲敲門的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.62,0:04:53.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且可以不用這樣的事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.22,0:04:57.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,既然都弄好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.54,0:04:59.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放在這兒就行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.06,0:05:00.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呃…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.53,0:05:04.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是什麼程式啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.36,0:05:08.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說了你也不懂的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.17,0:05:10.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是欺負人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.35,0:05:13.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我說你就讓我工作吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.38,0:05:18.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在臉紅什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.33,0:05:20.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒…沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.98,0:05:23.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打擾你工作了不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.01,0:05:25.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,告辭了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.82,0:05:27.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.44,0:05:28.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.98,0:05:39.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好喝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.65,0:05:43.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼…我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.90,0:05:44.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,騙人…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.36,0:05:56.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莫非你都看見了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.14,0:05:57.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,挺清楚地…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.77,0:06:00.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,深衣奈小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.84,0:06:02.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想談關於麻郁先生的事…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.75,0:06:04.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是的不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.44,0:06:06.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為這是我第一次遇見親人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.41,0:06:08.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,高興得忘乎所以了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.29,0:06:10.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我身上發生過很多事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.55,0:06:12.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也沒什麼好的回憶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.58,0:06:14.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以就更…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.07,0:06:17.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且看到麻鬱也很能幹
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.65,0:06:19.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,心地也不壞
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.55,0:06:22.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過連做夢都夢見他就有點讓我吃驚
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.49,0:06:24.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但不是那樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.58,0:06:26.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是那樣的 所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.40,0:06:29.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麻鬱有可能是親人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.46,0:06:30.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對對
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.31,0:06:33.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但也有可能是外人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.75,0:06:35.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,深衣奈小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.92,0:06:38.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果麻郁是外人你會怎麼辦？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.69,0:06:42.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.04,0:06:43.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,答案是肯定的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.64,0:06:46.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不一定會是那樣的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.09,0:06:49.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但如果真是外人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.67,0:06:51.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就得搬出這個家了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.52,0:06:55.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.99,0:06:57.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來是我會錯意
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.69,0:07:00.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你指什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.54,0:07:01.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.60,0:07:02.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我來應門
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.20,0:07:07.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們在這幹什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.18,0:07:09.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.87,0:07:11.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秘密會議
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.98,0:07:15.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請問是哪位？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.11,0:07:21.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,前輩？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.37,0:07:23.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.05,0:07:23.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,神城同學
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.09,0:07:34.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓神城同學完成的社團活動經費預算資料
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.26,0:07:37.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,約定好上星期做出來的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.07,0:07:41.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我還以為出了什麼問題呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.86,0:07:43.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.60,0:07:45.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是工作太忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.03,0:07:49.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能不能等到星期一？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.63,0:07:52.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這倒沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.03,0:07:53.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,十分感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.49,0:07:54.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請問…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.02,0:07:59.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是比麻郁高一級的前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.95,0:08:01.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,叫做織部椿
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.03,0:08:04.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,習慣這裏的生活了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.61,0:08:06.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,宮野深衣奈小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.47,0:08:08.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼知道我的名字？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.36,0:08:12.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們學生會會長的情報網可是很靈通的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.62,0:08:16.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,至於為何會那麼靈通那就是秘密了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.89,0:08:21.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請告訴森野會長請她請手下留情
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.85,0:08:25.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.03,0:08:26.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.38,0:08:29.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的事情已經說完了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.35,0:08:30.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.76,0:08:32.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麻鬱還有工作呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.85,0:08:35.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,叫得很親熱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.35,0:08:37.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.45,0:08:39.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們可是親人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.04,0:08:40.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.02,0:08:41.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別粘過來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.11,0:08:45.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是親人的話當然沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.14,0:08:47.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但也有可能是外人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.54,0:08:50.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果是外人的話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.43,0:08:55.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那看起來就像你在一昧地在引誘神城同學似的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.64,0:08:59.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才沒這回事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.52,0:09:00.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.42,0:09:02.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說回來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.49,0:09:03.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你沒其他事的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.50,0:09:06.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我送茶水來了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.36,0:09:09.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用麻煩的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.09,0:09:11.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是既然送來了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.23,0:09:13.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就不客氣…了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.13,0:09:19.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,並不是擺得上臺的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.70,0:09:23.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,脖子怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.68,0:09:28.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個…請不要問
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.16,0:09:29.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,深衣奈小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.25,0:09:30.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的表情好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.90,0:09:32.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是天生的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.53,0:09:34.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是…是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.16,0:09:37.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.67,0:09:40.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真好喝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.52,0:09:43.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是哪里的礦泉水？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.31,0:09:45.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是一般的自來水而已
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.47,0:09:46.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為我家很窮
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.65,0:09:49.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是因為你們來住的緣故
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.32,0:09:55.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,神城同學！對有可能是親人的人這麼說真是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.78,0:09:57.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.53,0:10:03.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也有可能是外人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.40,0:10:06.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我有點心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.17,0:10:08.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然是開了封的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.88,0:10:09.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Prech？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.75,0:10:10.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.76,0:10:12.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我最愛吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.96,0:10:17.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,神奇小子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.86,0:10:19.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.66,0:10:21.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.05,0:10:21.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.89,0:10:22.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,非常的可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.78,0:10:25.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們怎麼那麼鎮靜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.26,0:10:28.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙很奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.62,0:10:30.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,神城你不知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.63,0:10:34.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這孩子經常出現在這一帶的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.47,0:10:36.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請不要說得那麼輕鬆啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.67,0:10:40.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真不愧是發生過UFO騷亂的地方呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.70,0:10:43.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,學校的同學都叫他瑪麗耶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.87,0:10:44.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是瑪麗耶先生嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.98,0:10:49.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他有反應了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.63,0:10:51.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很奇怪呀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.02,0:10:52.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不覺得奇怪嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.43,0:10:53.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.98,0:10:56.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它帶著救生圈啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.01,0:10:57.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼關係 不是挺可愛的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.93,0:10:59.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他在吃Prech啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.68,0:11:02.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是雜食呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.01,0:11:03.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.27,0:11:05.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.79,0:11:06.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,工作…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.61,0:11:07.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,神城同學
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.21,0:11:10.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用介意我的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.81,0:11:11.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.72,0:11:13.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個奇怪的生物…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.54,0:11:16.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,工作可能會來不及的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.47,0:11:17.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.48,0:11:23.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要揮手
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.13,0:11:23.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.64,0:11:31.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麻郁回房工作去了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.47,0:11:34.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,前輩還不回去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.27,0:11:35.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對對
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.57,0:11:37.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我給忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.10,0:11:39.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我對媽媽說去神城家
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.80,0:11:42.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,結果她硬要我帶這蕎麥面來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.18,0:11:43.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.45,0:11:44.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,非常感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.99,0:11:45.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.66,0:11:49.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽她教了我作法 所以
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.73,0:11:51.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早有預謀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.84,0:11:53.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.08,0:11:54.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.37,0:11:56.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,深衣奈小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.49,0:12:00.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以省掉一頓午飯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.29,0:12:01.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是呀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.20,0:12:04.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只剩一小時了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.49,0:12:08.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是樓下不要緊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.29,0:12:11.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,搞什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.37,0:12:12.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天也是凶日嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.55,0:12:14.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.42,0:12:15.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是神城
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.07,0:12:16.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.87,0:12:17.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.80,0:12:18.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.68,0:12:19.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.73,0:12:43.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在那邊的莫非是森野同學？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.40,0:12:49.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 風見老師
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.13,0:12:51.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在這種地方幹什麼呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.86,0:12:55.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,觀鳥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.74,0:13:01.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是騙人的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.14,0:13:03.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是當然的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.35,0:13:12.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,送蕎麥面給我們真是很感謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.59,0:13:14.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,料理我會來做的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.83,0:13:18.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是來教你美味的做法的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.30,0:13:21.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是說我做的很難吃嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.40,0:13:22.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你擅長做料理嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.88,0:13:25.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是我自誇
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.35,0:13:29.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,昨天和前天麻鬱吃了都說很好吃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.55,0:13:30.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.37,0:13:34.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別作出一副出乎意料的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.16,0:13:36.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼生氣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.05,0:13:37.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,簡直就像是吃醋一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.08,0:13:40.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算是那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.74,0:13:42.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又有什麼好說的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.41,0:13:44.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可能是親人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.73,0:13:47.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以有種很危險的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.68,0:13:50.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也可能是外人所以沒關係的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.69,0:13:54.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,外人住在這個家裏不是很奇怪嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.23,0:13:56.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也可能是親人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.50,0:13:58.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪種可能比較好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.56,0:14:02.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說來前輩認為哪種可能比較好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.67,0:14:04.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪種呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.76,0:14:07.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣下去會沒完沒了的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.83,0:14:09.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蕎麥一人分一半怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.52,0:14:12.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.56,0:14:17.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鍋子借我用一下行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.82,0:14:19.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過只有小的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.52,0:14:22.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係只要作一人份就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.97,0:14:25.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打擾一下…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.96,0:14:26.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.41,0:14:35.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.17,0:14:38.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,春子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.70,0:14:41.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥也一起去不好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.36,0:14:42.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.46,0:14:45.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天是去同學家
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.16,0:14:48.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼沒有面鹵？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.89,0:14:50.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為窮嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.86,0:14:52.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別這麼說嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.46,0:14:53.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.52,0:15:00.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是…是我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.78,0:15:01.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誰
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.58,0:15:02.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是樺戀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.76,0:15:04.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我能進來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.28,0:15:05.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.48,0:15:06.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正好完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.96,0:15:07.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 來得正好…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.91,0:15:15.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呃…麻郁的前輩和深衣奈小姐 以很恐怖的感覺在做料理
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.93,0:15:19.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,背上還跑出老虎和獅子的氣焰
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.00,0:15:20.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.28,0:15:22.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都說是老虎和獅子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.62,0:15:24.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裏沒有那種東西
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.94,0:15:26.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然如此…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.62,0:15:28.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,稍微鎮靜點
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.47,0:15:30.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我有話和你說
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.06,0:15:31.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,坐這邊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.95,0:15:34.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是 失禮了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.37,0:15:38.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,樺戀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.99,0:15:45.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你把這裏的電話告訴了養育你的家人了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.25,0:15:46.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.52,0:15:50.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,昨天打了公用電話給叔叔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.08,0:15:53.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把這個家裏的電話告訴了他
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.02,0:15:54.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可以的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.49,0:15:56.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他打電話來了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.58,0:16:01.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我說 他打電話來了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.26,0:16:03.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莫非是叔叔打來的？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.00,0:16:06.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是關於道謝的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.47,0:16:07.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我接了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.52,0:16:11.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被告知了大概的情況
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.95,0:16:13.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你叔叔的公司不太妙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.90,0:16:21.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,經濟不景氣真討厭呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.37,0:16:22.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.89,0:16:26.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但總算知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.57,0:16:32.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上女校的樺戀為什麼會在讀書的時候尋到這裏來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.26,0:16:34.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.19,0:16:35.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有告訴你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.83,0:16:37.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒必要道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.72,0:16:38.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.35,0:16:43.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大概樺戀的叔叔也有些事沒有告訴樺戀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.15,0:16:47.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖說有些俗氣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.95,0:16:53.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你叔叔為了維持公司似乎太過於吃力了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.54,0:16:57.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為可能會困擾樺戀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.55,0:17:00.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就讓你到這張照片上的家來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.40,0:17:03.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我稍許有些感覺到了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.91,0:17:11.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔他一直說不要一個人旅行那是很危險的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.68,0:17:13.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我總是心不在焉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.55,0:17:18.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但他突然准許我了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.19,0:17:21.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.46,0:17:25.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,離開了家的樺戀就拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.88,0:17:27.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請儘量照顧她
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.35,0:17:29.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他是這麼說的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.70,0:17:31.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麻郁先生
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.06,0:17:32.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔他…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.15,0:17:34.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放心好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.10,0:17:37.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他說沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.97,0:17:38.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.73,0:17:44.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但他說有可能不能打電話來了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.68,0:17:48.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.44,0:17:52.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有…他說對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.58,0:17:57.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔…叔叔他…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.43,0:18:14.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你叔叔很慈祥吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.74,0:18:20.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可能沒有什麼說服力 但…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.50,0:18:22.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要緊的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.02,0:18:22.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要緊的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.96,0:18:26.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,住在這裏就好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.58,0:18:28.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為住在這裏也行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.84,0:18:30.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.68,0:18:35.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麻郁先生有可能是外人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.17,0:18:36.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.15,0:18:37.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可能會是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.00,0:18:43.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是我和樺戀有著相同顏色的眼瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.38,0:18:46.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.16,0:18:48.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,住在這裏就好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.82,0:19:00.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不會拋棄的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.73,0:19:04.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,絕對不會
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.69,0:19:12.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麻鬱\N神城同學
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.15,0:19:23.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.46,0:19:26.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是我想問的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.78,0:19:27.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又不敲門
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.89,0:19:28.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又把飯給摔了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.98,0:19:30.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.76,0:19:36.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.37,0:19:41.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,忸…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.28,0:19:45.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,神城同學
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.64,0:19:49.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你幹了些什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.08,0:19:49.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.91,0:19:51.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好好聽我說明
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.20,0:19:55.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,樺戀哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.16,0:19:57.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道你強迫她…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.05,0:19:58.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是誤會
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.48,0:20:00.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們要聽我說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.28,0:20:00.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.91,0:20:01.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,深衣奈
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.96,0:20:04.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不敢相信
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.36,0:20:07.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,神城竟然是會做出這種事的人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.88,0:20:11.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,稍微心動的我簡直就是傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.33,0:20:13.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們聽我說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.77,0:20:15.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.84,0:20:19.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幹得漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.54,0:20:20.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,神城同學
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.07,0:20:39.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,白天的事真是嚇了我一大跳呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.40,0:20:44.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過仔細想想也覺得那種事不可能會發生呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.79,0:20:46.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當然
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.06,0:20:47.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.00,0:20:54.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拿出精神來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.13,0:20:59.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是能住在這裏真是太好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.18,0:20:59.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.29,0:21:03.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也是一樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.87,0:21:05.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,深衣奈小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.49,0:21:09.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麻郁先生可能是親人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.78,0:21:13.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大概…是我們中一個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.90,0:21:15.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.57,0:21:19.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也可能是外人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.13,0:21:24.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,菊池嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.57,0:21:25.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是神城
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.96,0:21:31.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天要傳的那份資料明天早上才交行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.97,0:21:33.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.51,0:21:36.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很努力地在做
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.01,0:21:38.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是有些地方卡住了而已
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.78,0:21:41.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很用心地在做
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.99,0:21:43.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有偷懶！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.59,0:21:45.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.23,0:21:47.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可能是親人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.50,0:21:50.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.76,0:21:55.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也可能是外人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.90,0:23:24.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(400,370)\fs40\fn幼圓\3c&Hb351cf\bord3}對你溫柔
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.25,0:23:27.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,深衣奈小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.11,0:23:30.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們不能夠總是依靠麻郁先生的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.80,0:23:33.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看看這個兼職情報志
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.00,0:23:35.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裏寫麻鬱所上的學校招募兼職耶
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.58,0:23:39.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過寫著對象是十八歲以上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.11,0:23:40.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我的話就沒問題的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.64,0:23:43.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那毫無根據的自信是從哪里來的？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.15,0:23:43.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你這是什麼意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.91,0:23:45.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼特別意思的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.96,0:23:47.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Onegai Twins 第四話
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.76,0:23:48.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對你溫柔
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.99,0:23:50.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定要看噢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.05,0:23:51.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下一回也是 Twins！
